import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { MissionlistComponent } from './missionlist/missionlist.component'; import { Mission } from 'src/models/mission'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = '101314570-lab-test2-comp3133'; constructor(private _MissionListComponent: MissionlistComponent) {} missionList: Mission[] = []; ngOnInit() { this._MissionListComponent.getMissionList().subscribe( data => { this.missionList = data; } ) } }
